== Change log ==

Version 2.1.7 - 09/15/2017
---------------------------------
- WooCommerce 3 compatibility

Version 2.1.6 - 04/06/2017
---------------------------------
- Now fiscal code is no longer verified for companies
- Now customer type is displayed by label in dashboard

Version 2.1.5 - 03/30/2017
---------------------------------
- Now company name is displayed in single order edit form
- Now custom meta is displayed in admin new order email

Version 2.1.4 - 03/30/2017
---------------------------------
- Now the plugin will save the value for "request invoice" checkbox
- The custom meta are displayed in order listing
- The custom meta are displayed in order listing

Version 2.1.3 - 03/22/2017
---------------------------------
- Now the plugin don't try to validate the custom fields if the customer has not requested the billing

Version 2.1.2 - 03/15/2017
---------------------------------
- Moved some checkout fields around
- Added "*" to required fields
- Refactoring of Migration inclusion
- Now customer type, vat and fiscal code are saved alongside the order and displayed in dashboard

Version 2.1.1 - 03/10/2017
---------------------------------
- Added Migration class

Version 2.1.0 - 02/09/2017
---------------------------------
- WBF is not included anymore

Version 2.0.0 - 12/02/2016
---------------------------------
- Refactoring
- Tweak: now company field is displayed below fiscal code